THAT WE WANT TO LIVE.

28:55.460 --> 29:01.831
AND WE TRAIN TO FIGHT
AGAINST ALL OF OUR ENEMIES.

29:03.500 --> 29:05.468
YAAH!

29:08.180 --> 29:10.535
WE TAKE WHAT WE WANT.

29:10.580 --> 29:15.813
BUT WE--WE ALWAYS
DEFEND OUR TREASURE.

29:20.350 --> 29:22.818
AND THAT'S WHY
YOU TAKE THE BLOOD OATH.

29:22.860 --> 29:25.852
