THE TREASURE

29:25.890 --> 29:27.357
TO THE DEATH.

29:27.390 --> 29:28.789
TO THE DEATH.

29:28.830 --> 29:30.525
AND BEWARE THE CURSE.

29:30.560 --> 29:34.530
TO ANY PIRATE WHO WOULD
GO AGAINST THE OATH,

29:34.570 --> 29:36.299
MAY HE BE VISITED
BY THE GHOSTS

29:36.340 --> 29:39.969
OF ALL THE PIRATES
WHO HAVE GONE BEFORE.

29:52.320 --> 29:57.189
LELAND KNEW THE--
THE POWER OF THE CURSE.

29:57.220 --> 29:59.381
WHO'S LELAND?

30:02.330 --> 30:06.096
WE HAVE TO DEFEND
THE TREASURE.

30:06.130 --> 30:12.899
