THE TREASURE SOMEPLACE ELSE.

30:23.550 --> 30:25.848
YOU GOTTA DO IT.

30:25.890 --> 30:28.279
IT'S REALLY IMPORTANT.

30:30.990 --> 30:35.359
AND THEN THAT MORNING,
HE WENT DOWN TO THE TREASURE

30:35.400 --> 30:37.425
TO STAND GUARD, AND...

30:44.640 --> 30:47.564
AND I WAS--I WAS
TOO AFRAID,

30:47.610 --> 30:50.408
SO I STAYED HOME,
AND IT...

30:58.690 --> 31:00.908
I BROKE THE OATH.

31:06.560 --> 31:10.121
