31:40.460 --> 31:41.950
I NEED TO G0.
I JUST--

31:42.000 --> 31:43.126
NO. YOU CAN'T GO.

31:43.160 --> 31:45.162
NO, YOU CAN'T.

31:45.200 --> 31:47.521
