THE BREAD WAS NEVER BAKED.

32:41.720 --> 32:43.585
ALVEZ: YEAH,
AT SOME POINT, IT'S TIME

32:43.620 --> 32:45.383
TO STOP THINKING ABOUT
WHAT'S POSSIBLE

32:45.430 --> 32:47.227
AND START THINKING
ABOUT WHAT'S LIKELY.

32:47.260 --> 32:49.751
WHICH, FOR ME,
IS THAT LELAND IS DEAD

32:49.800 --> 32:51.995
AND HAS BEEN DEAD
FOR A LONG, LONG TIME.

32:52.030 --> 32:53.566
JJ: WHICH WOULD LEAVE US WHERE?

32:53.600 --> 32:55.397
WELL, EMILY SAID
THAT PETERS TOLD HER

32:55.440 --> 32:58.568
LELAND HAD OTHER KIDS
HE'D PLAY PIRATES WITH.

33:00.570 --> 33:01.730
RELEASE THE GENIE.

33:01.780 --> 33:03.407
LELAND PETERS--
DID HIS JUVIE TROUBLE

33:03.440 --> 33:05.146
EVER INVOLVE
ANOTHER KID?

33:05.180 --> 33:06.147
UH, YEAH.
A WHOLE GROUP OF KIDS.

33:06.180 --> 33:07.408
THEY RAN IN A PACK.

33:07.450 --> 33:08.747
DOES ONE NAME POP UP
MORE THAN THE OTHERS?

33:08.780 --> 33:11.783
OH. LIKE B-14
IN A BINGO PARLOR.

33:11.820 --> 33:14.687
JESS CARNEY. HE AND LELAND
WERE THICK AS THIEVES.

33:14.720 --> 33:17.553
LITERALLY. STOLE STU FF,
TRUANCY.

33:17.590 --> 33:18.557
BUT THIS IS WEIRD.

33:18.590 --> 33:21.525
AT AGE 14, JESS--POOF--

33:21.560 --> 33:23.653
LIKE DISAPPEARS.

33:23.700 --> 33:26.021
HIS BEHAVIOR TOOK
A VIOLENT TURN

33:26.070 --> 33:28.061
SHORTLY AFTER
THE CANYON FLOODED.

33:28.100 --> 33:30.068
HIS PARENTS COULDN'T
CONTROL HIM ANYMORE.

33:30.100 --> 33:31.601
AND AS SOON AS THE MYSTERY
PRESENTS ITSELF,

33:31.640 --> 33:33.062
THE MYSTERY IS SOLVED.

33:33.110 --> 33:34.737
JESS WAS INSTITUTIONALIZED
OUT OF STATE

33:34.780 --> 33:36.338
AND PUT ON ANTIDEPRESSANTS.

33:36.380 --> 33:38.109
THAT WOULD EXPLAIN
THE ARRESTED DEVELOPMENT.

33:38.150 --> 33:40.106
HE WAS MEDICATED
AND ISOLATED

33:40.150 --> 33:41.742
DURING SOME
CRUCIAL FORMATIVE YEARS.

33:41.780 --> 33:45.511
JESS CARNEY RETURNED TO
CALIFORNIA WHEN HE WAS 24

33:45.550 --> 33:47.780
AND WORKED ODD JOBS
IN AND AROUND SAN DIEGO.

33:47.820 --> 33:51.654
AND THEN...SUDDENLY LEI-T
THE AREA ABOUT A MONTH AGO.

33:51.690 --> 33:53.658
THAT'S RIGHT AROUND THE TIME
THE KILLINGS STARTED.

33:53.690 --> 33:55.419
DO WE KNOW WHERE
JESS IS NOW?

33:55.460 --> 33:57.553
OH. OH, WE DO NOT.
AI-TER HE LEI-T SAN DIEGO,

33:57.600 --> 33:58.760
HE--HE--POOF--
VANISHED AGAIN.

33:58.800 --> 34:01.132
IT'S LIKE A RE-POOF,
I GUESS YOU'D CALL IT.

34:01.170 --> 34:02.797
IS THERE A RECENT
PHOTO OF CARNEY?

34:02.840 --> 34:05.604
THE BEST I HAVE
IS A DMV PHOTO
FROM 6 YEARS AGO.

34:05.640 --> 34:07.631
SENDING IT NOW.

34:39.210 --> 34:41.405
IT'S TIME TO GO.

34:41.440 --> 34:44.238
LELAND IS WAITING
FOR US DOWN THERE.

34:44.280 --> 34:47.204
IT'S TIME WE JOIN HIM.

34:58.890 --> 35:00.687
